<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-24"><a href="#Existence_des_atomes"><span class="tocnumber">3.2</span> <span class="toctext">Existence des atomes</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-3 tocsection-25"><a href="#Modèle_planétaire"><span class="tocnumber">3.2.1</span> <span class="toctext">Modèle planétaire</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-3 tocsection-26"><a href="#Atomisme_et_anti-atomisme"><span class="tocnumber">3.2.2</span> <span class="toctext">Atomisme et anti-atomisme</span></a></li>
