    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle \Delta m=4m_{H}-m_{He}=(6,6900-6,6459)*10^{-27}=0,0441*10^{-27}{}kg\;}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/43412da7d09bd9096ec111cc06648592182bd6d5" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:69.014ex; height:3.176ex;" alt="{\displaystyle \Delta m=4m_{H}-m_{He}=(6,6900-6,6459)*10^{-27}=0,0441*10^{-27}{}kg\;}"/></span></center>
<p>Soit un peu moins de 7 millièmes de la masse de 4 atomes d'hydrogène&#160;:
</p>
<center><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle {\frac {\Delta m}{4*m_{H}}}={\frac {0,0441}{4*1,6725}}=0,0065}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
